Awtication</em></a>女演员Sophie sophie Thatcher的合作曲目。</p><p>该项目是由总部位于阿什维尔（Asheville）的录音室落下太阳组织（Drop Sun Drop Sun）组织的，后者在观看他们努力从飓风中造成的伤害中恢复过来后，受到启发来帮助当地艺术社区。</p><p> “这些以前未发行的曲目的显着广度反映了太阳的核心原则，促进了一个供艺术家自由无限创造的环境，” <a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/mj-lenderman-animal-collective-contribute-to-new-asheville-benefit-album-listen/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Pitchfork</em></a>的太阳创始人亚当·麦克丹尼尔（Adam McDaniel）解释说。 “成为阿什维尔艺术社区的一种资源，产生了美好的，持久的关系，类似的歌曲，以及在艰难时期进行交流和应对的平台。我们很高兴与您分享这些独家歌曲。” </p><figure id="attachment_3826048" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3826048" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3826048" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/MJ-Lenderman.-CREDIT_-Griffin-Lotz_Rolling-Stone-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3826048" class="wp-caption-text"> MJ Lenderman。图片来源：Griffin Lotz/通过Getty Images的滚石</figcaption></figure><p>Helene飓风<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deadly-hurricane-helene-hits-live-events-in-the-us-3798428">影响了将在美国东南部举行的各种节目和节日</a>，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/new